        "data": "Worked Example 2 — Interior angle of a regular hexagon:\nStep 1: Number of sides, n = 6\nStep 2: Sum of interior angles = (6 - 2) × 180 = 4 × 180 = 720°\nStep 3: Each interior angle = 720 / 6 = 120°"
