        "data": "<b>Hydrolysis of Disaccharides:</b>\nSucrose + H<sub>2</sub>O → Glucose + Fructose (in presence of acid or enzyme sucrase)\nMaltose + H<sub>2</sub>O → 2 Glucose (enzyme maltase)"
