        "data": "<b>6. Relationship Between Organs</b>\n- The legislature passes laws, which the executive implements.\n- The judiciary interprets laws and checks unconstitutional actions.\n- The executive proposes bills and budgets to the legislature.\n- Each organ monitors the others to maintain balance and prevent abuse of power."
